import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  

export default class MDXContent extends React.Component {
  constructor(props) {
    super(props)
    this.layout = null
  }
  render() {
    const { components, ...props } = this.props

    return <MDXTag
             name="wrapper"
             
             components={components}><MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"keyboard-shortcuts"}}>{`Keyboard Shortcuts`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"navigation"}}>{`Navigation`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"navigation-shortcut-reference"}}>{`Navigation shortcut reference`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="table" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="thead" components={components} parentName="table">
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="thead">
<MDXTag name="th" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Shortcut`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="th" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Function`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tbody" components={components} parentName="table">
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`←`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Change to previous page index`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`→`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Change to next page index`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`⌘ + ←`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Close sidebar`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`⌘ + →`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Open sidebar`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`↑`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Move up sidebar option tree`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`↓`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Move down sidebar option tree`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"utilities"}}>{`Utilities`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"utility-shortcut-reference"}}>{`Utility shortcut reference`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="table" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="thead" components={components} parentName="table">
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="thead">
<MDXTag name="th" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Shortcut`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="th" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Function`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="tbody" components={components} parentName="table">
<MDXTag name="tr" components={components} parentName="tbody">
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`⌘ + s`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="td" components={components} parentName="tr" props={{"align":null}}>{`Save current project`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
           </MDXTag>
  }
}
